8. Minimal operating protocol

When new data comes in, run this:

Step 1

Classify the input:
	•	what type is it?
	•	how real is it?
	•	how noisy is it?

Step 2

Route it:
	•	symbolic data goes to Dragonfly/Raven first
	•	outcome data goes to Mirror/Sisyphus first
	•	decision data goes to Spider/Hound/Mirror/Raven

Step 3

Produce one output:
	•	insight
	•	recommendation
	•	artifact
	•	doctrine

Step 4

Log the outcome later.

Step 5

Update the rules if a pattern repeats.

