10. What this gives you

This architecture fixes several problems at once:
	•	stops data overload from becoming mush
	•	separates symbol from proof
	•	gives Pantheon a real learning loop
	•	creates products people and AI can actually use
	•	turns the repo into a refinery, not just an archive

The deeper win is this:

the Pantheon stops being merely a place where ideas accumulate, and becomes a plant that converts raw experience into usable power.

